item.title: cocada
item.description: Ingredients 2 cups dulce de coco 2 tablespoons melted butter 2 beaten eggs 2 ounces peeled almonds Directions Add the butter and eggs to the dulce de coco. Pour into a flat greased mold. Garnish with almonds. Bake over moderate heat for 20 minutes.
